{"id":26739,"date":"2024-09-25T03:23:03","date_gmt":"2024-09-24T21:53:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=26739"},"modified":"2024-10-21T23:29:53","modified_gmt":"2024-10-21T17:59:53","slug":"which-colour-is-best-for-hall","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall\/","title":{"rendered":"Which Colour Is Best For Hall As Per Vastu?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>A hall is the most important place in your home as it\u2019s the first space people notice. Make it look inviting and mood-enhancing by using Vastu-compliant colour(s) for its walls, furniture and furnishings. Read more to find out.&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your hall is the \u2018face\u2019 of your home and it is the first thing that your visitors lay eyes on when they step in. Therefore, you need to ensure that it makes a lasting and positive first impression.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Add to this, the colour element of Vastu and you\u2019ll be able to benefit from it long-term in terms of good health, prosperity, successful career and relationships as well. <em>Isn\u2019t it great?&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A hallway is also considered as a functional space as it acts as a room connector and as an extra utilitarian\/display area too. This is a space that you can easily convert to a mini library or home office. Here are a few blogs\/guides that can help you smartly and effectively design your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/\">hall\u2019s interiors<\/a>. Moving on, now let\u2019s get into the crux of this blog.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" data-id=\"26740\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030017\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-yellow-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Which colour is best for hall where yellow signifies communication, intelligence and positivity \" class=\"wp-image-26740\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030017\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-yellow-hall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030017\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-yellow-hall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030017\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-yellow-hall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030017\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-yellow-hall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Yellow signifies communication, intelligence and positivity which makes it an ideal colour for the hall and living room combo<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which Colour Paint Is The Best For A Hall According To Vastu?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to Vastu Shastra principles, each direction or room of the house has a specific colour attached to it, and each colour has its own physical and mental benefits for its homeowners. A general rule of thumb here is to avoid dark colours as they make the hall look even smaller and give it a muted feel. In brief, some suitable Vastu colours for each direction of the house are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>North \u2192 <\/strong>Light Green, Green&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>East \u2192 <\/strong>Light Blue, White<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>West \u2192 <\/strong>White, Blue&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>South \u2192 <\/strong>Yellow, Light Red<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>North-East \u2192 <\/strong>Light Blue (IDEAL LOCATION FOR HALL)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>North-West \u2192 <\/strong>White, Light Grey, Cream (IDEAL LOCATION FOR HALL)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>South-East \u2192 <\/strong>Silver, Light Pink, Light Orange<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>South-West \u2192<\/strong> Light Brown, Beige, Cream, Peach, Mud Colour&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" data-id=\"26741\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030246\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-according-to-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"which colour is best for hall where Light grey signifies concentration and tranquillity \" class=\"wp-image-26741\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030246\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-according-to-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030246\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-according-to-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030246\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-according-to-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030246\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-according-to-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Light grey signifies concentration and tranquillity which is very much required in a hall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Speaking specifically for your hall, these are the best colours according to the principles of Vastu:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Green <\/strong>\u2192 Green is a great choice for the hall\/hall and living room combo as it stands for healing, creation, nature, growth and prosperity. It is also soothing and known to reduce stress and anxiety as it mimics natural elements.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>White <\/strong>\u2192 White signifies a sense of cleanliness, privacy and simplicity. It also represents intimacy and freshness making it the perfect choice for your hall that\u2019s a hub of conversations and social gatherings.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" data-id=\"26742\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030428\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Which colour is best for hall irrespective of the colours that you use on the sidewalls \" class=\"wp-image-26742\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030428\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030428\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030428\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030428\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The ceiling should always be painted white irrespective of the colours that you use on the sidewalls of the hall\/any other room of the house<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Light Red<\/strong> \u2192 Light red signifies energy, comfort, warmth, action and vibrance so you can use this colour for the hall. It looks bold, represents passion and also makes the occupant feel more energised.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Yellow<\/strong> \u2192 Yellow represents power, self-esteem, purity, communication and optimism. It is also a bright and fun colour for the hall and is recommended for those going through a tough time.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Blue <\/strong>\u2192 Blue gives out a calm and pleasing vibe. It signifies emotion, beauty and truth. It also helps in healing anxiety and pain and gives you beachy and breezy vibes, hence it is the perfect choice for the hall.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" data-id=\"26744\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030859\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-blue-room.jpg\" alt=\"Which colour is best for hall which brings in positive vibrations to spaces\" class=\"wp-image-26744\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030859\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-blue-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030859\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-blue-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030859\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-blue-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25030859\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-blue-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Using more than one (max. three) Vastu colours in the hall in a balanced way brings in positive vibrations to spaces<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Light Brown <\/strong>\u2192 Light brown adds a splash of elegance and sophistication to the hall and it represents tranquillity, wisdom, comfort, stability in life and inner peace. It is also the most common colour used for the hall.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" data-id=\"26745\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031103\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-2.jpg\" alt=\"Which colour is best for hall where Light brown colour brings in nature\u2019s vibes and introduces happiness \" class=\"wp-image-26745\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031103\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-2.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031103\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-2-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031103\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-2-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031103\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-2-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Light brown colour brings in nature\u2019s vibes and introduces happiness and satisfaction in the space. <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Beige <\/strong>\u2192 Beige brings positivity and relaxation into the hall. It signifies stability, warmth and also acts as a perfect backdrop for your elegant and colourful home decor.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" data-id=\"26746\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031231\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-3.jpg\" alt=\"Which colour is best for hall if All pastel colours are an ideal choice for the hall\" class=\"wp-image-26746\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031231\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-3.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031231\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-3-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031231\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-3-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25031231\/which-colour-is-best-for-hall-3-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">All pastel colours are an ideal choice for the hall as they are light and blend in seamlessly with the existing theme of the house without any modifications<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That\u2019s all there is! Hope this blog has provided you with some useful information on colours that are best suited for your hall to make it more Vastu-compliant. So, hurry up, experiment with our recommended colour combinations and make your hall leave a lasting first impression on your friends and family. Good luck!<br>If you\u2019re still confused regarding the same, get in touch with our interior design experts at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Design Cafe <\/a>and they\u2019ll gladly guide you through this process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about which colour is best for hall, also have a look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/colour-combination-for-hall\/\">colour combinations for hall<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Personalised Dream Home Interiors<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get